## 11) Uu tien tiep theo (van hanh queue/Celery)

Muc tieu: ngung tinh trang pending/queued gia, phat hien som su co Redis/Celery, va giam tac nghen do timeout/retry.

P0. Runtime health check cho Redis/Celery:
- Backend them endpoint health van hanh (VD: `/api/v1/runtime-health`):
  - ping Redis broker/result backend.
  - ping Celery worker (co node reply khong).
  - check beat heartbeat age (co gui task scheduler trong cua so cho phep khong).
- Output gom `status`, `degraded_reasons`, `timestamp` de UI de parse.

P1. UI canh bao ro rang khi worker/beat mat ket noi:
- Dashboard/Monitors hien banner canh bao neu runtime health khong `ok`.
- Neu user bam `Run Check` trong luc runtime degraded:
  - van cho queue (de khong pha API behavior),
  - nhung hien canh bao "task co the bi tre do worker/beat/redis khong on dinh".

P2. Profile va tuning interval/timeout/retry:
- Thu thap metric check run:
  - p50/p95/p99 `response_time_ms`, timeout rate, retry rate, queue age.
- Rule tam de tranh nghen:
  - timeout_seconds <= interval_seconds * 0.6
  - max_retries toi da 1 cho monitor timeout cao
  - canh bao monitor co `timeout_ratio` cao.
- De xuat thay doi default an toan dua tren profile (khong fix cung khi chua co so lieu).

## 12) Runtime hardening (done)

Muc tieu: giam tai ket noi Redis/Celery, chan duplicate process khi restart local, va giu deploy van hanh on dinh voi Docker Compose.

Da lam xong:
- Harden config Celery (`backend/app/core/config.py`, `backend/app/workers/celery_app.py`):
  - `celery_broker_pool_limit=2`
  - `celery_broker_heartbeat_seconds=30`
  - `celery_broker_health_check_interval_seconds=30`
  - `celery_worker_prefetch_multiplier=1`
  - `celery_broker_retry_on_startup=true`
- Harden command Compose production (`docker-compose.prod.yml`):
  - worker chay voi `--without-gossip --without-mingle` de giam ket noi/control traffic khong can thiet.
  - beat co `--pidfile=/tmp/celerybeat.pid` de tranh race process.
- Them script local idempotent:
  - `scripts/restart_celery_runtime.ps1`: stop toan bo process celery cu -> verify khong con duplicate -> start lai worker + beat.
  - `scripts/check_celery_runtime.ps1`: check nhanh so process worker/beat va canh bao duplicate/missing.
- Cap nhat runbook README:
  - bo sung lenh restart/check runtime an toan cho local.
  - nhac ro Celery decoupled va cach tranh pending/queued gia do duplicate process.
 - Khong them wrapper script moi cho safe-restart (tranh du abstraction):
  - chot huong dan strict flow truc tiep trong README (preflight -> guarded restart -> health check -> celery strict topology check).
 - Fix local script issue tren Windows:
  - bo Unix pidfile arg `--pidfile=/tmp/celerybeat.pid` khoi local restart scripts de beat khong crash.

## 13) Dashboard latency + runtime false-alert (done)

Van de ghi nhan:
- Dashboard load cham/treo du lieu sau login du cac endpoint dashboard core van nhanh.
- Runtime health co luc bao `celery_worker_unreachable` du worker van dang chay.

Nguyen nhan goc:
- Frontend dashboard truoc day dung `Promise.all` cho ca block, nen chi can `GET /runtime/health` cham/timeout la ca page bi doi.
- Runtime health check worker dung `celery inspect ping` gay false-negative va do tre lon trong mot so local runtime states.

Fix da trien khai:
- Backend runtime health:
  - bo path `inspect ping`, chuyen sang worker heartbeat key (`moni:runtime:worker:last_seen_at`) + beat heartbeat key.
  - them timeout guard cho redis/heartbeat reads de endpoint khong treo dai.
  - them warm-up fallback sau restart de giam false alert trong cua so dau.
- Worker ping task:
  - cap nhat ca beat heartbeat va worker heartbeat trong cung task scheduler.
- Frontend dashboard:
  - tach runtime panel khoi critical path:
    - core dashboard data load truoc.
    - runtime panel load nen (khong block first paint).
  - dung `Promise.allSettled` cho runtime calls.
  - them cache TTL ngan:
    - runtime health: 10s
    - queue profile: 15s

Ket qua sau fix:
- Dashboard khong con bi block boi `runtime/health`.
- Runtime health phan anh dung hon (giam canh bao `celery_worker_unreachable` gia).
- UX vao dashboard nhanh hon ro rang, van giu canh bao van hanh.

